│ proceeds to lane 1 (`LV: vectorizing VPBB:pred.store.if in BB:pred.store.if1`), it         │
│ crashes.\n\n### 3. Root Cause Analysis\n\nThe root cause lies in how the `SCALAR-STEPS`    │
│ VPValue (`vp<%5>`) is handled during the execution of the `VPReplicateRecipe`.\n\nA        │
│ `SCALAR-STEPS` VPValue is a special kind of value that doesn't have a single vector        │
